examples.en: I find him to be obnoxious.
Some teenagers were being loud and obnoxious.
He said some really obnoxious things about his ex-girlfriend at the party.
Although he's not the first person to blow his own horn, he's about the most obnoxious blower I've ever met.
Maybe if that television station replaced its obnoxious news anchor, it wouldn't get consistently whopped in the ratings.
